/* Table: "CON_Original" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_Original"
(
"OriginalID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"OriginalSAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"OriginalContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"StartDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"ActualEndDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
constraint PK_CON_ORIGINAL primary key ("OriginalID")
);

comment on table "CON_Original" is
'记录合同草稿原合同信息';
